@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant ConfigurationService
participant RulesEngine
participant BOMService
participant QuoteService
participant Storage (S3/Postgres/DynamoDB)

User -> Frontend: Create from Enquiry
Frontend -> ConfigurationService: POST /configurations (prefill from enquiry)
ConfigurationService -> Storage: Persist configuration (Postgres), session (DynamoDB)
Frontend -> Frontend: Open editor, connect to SignalR
User -> Frontend: Make change (delta)
Frontend -> RulesEngine: UpdateConfiguration(sessionId, change) [via SignalR]
RulesEngine -> Storage: Get applicable rules (cache Redis)
RulesEngine --> Frontend: ValidationResult (errors/warnings/suggestions)
User -> Frontend: Save Draft
Frontend -> ConfigurationService: POST /bom/generate
BOMService -> Storage: Read product catalog
BOMService --> Storage: Write BOM to S3
Frontend -> ConfigurationService: POST /quote/generate
QuoteService -> PricingService: Apply pricing & exchange rates
QuoteService --> Storage: Write Quote PDF to S3
Storage --> Frontend: Return links
@enduml